author: veithen
msg: Fix a minor unit test issue (invalid usage of a monitor) that doesn't cause any failures, but that unnecessarily delays test completion by 45 seconds.

author: veithen
msg: Remove the Java 1.5 profile (we don't support Java 1.5 builds anymore) and promote the settings in the Java 1.6 profile so that they applied to Java > 1.6 as well. This should fix most of the build issues with Java 1.7.
